<h3>Our Story</h3>
<p>Founded by Mr. Ram Hari in the year 2020AD, Snap-Snap has evolved into a
successful business which has gained the support of many people.
We have captured countless memories for our clients and have achieved positive
feedbacks. All our clients have been very satisfied with our work
and have praised us for our team spirit as well as our team work. Here we believe
that everything is possible when we are united and we try to give
the clients what they actually want. We also prefer communicating with the
clients about their ideas so that we can provide them the best services.
</p>
<h3>Our Mission</h3>
<p>We aim to capture the special moments and also try to capture the essence of
the event. During wedding and some other cultural events we try to capture the
uniqueness of the ritual. We also give preference to the guests who are
attending the event and try to capture each and everyone that has attended
the event.</p>
<h3>What sets us apart</h3>
<p> What sets us apart is our unique blend of technical expertise, artistic vision,
and personalized service. We understand that every client is unique, and we strive to
tailor our approach to meet their individual needs and preferences. We also pay great
attention to the essence of the event and act according to the need of the event</p>
